The paper deals with information complexity, which is a topic in computational complexity theory (cs.CC). It also involves information theory (cs.IT) and the analysis of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The study of communication complexity, which is related to information complexity, falls under both cs.CC and cs.DM (discrete mathematics). The paper also involves optimization and probability theory, which are topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG).
